Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Band of Seven are\nall together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:13.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their leader, Bankotsu,\nis their strongest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His huge halberd and Inuyasha's\NTetsusaiga are about to clash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:20.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the wolf comes\nbefore the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move it, you wimpy wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found you....Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see you have brute strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be the last\nof the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm Bankotsu the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ganging up on one wimpy wolf, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! No one's ganging up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's the one who almost\nlost his Sacred Jewel shards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not that stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So they've come.\NThey're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}bastards....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've had your way\nfor long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll send you back to your graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to avenge\NMukotsu and Kyokotsu's deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems the one with the large\nhalberd is the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, although he looks\nlike the youngest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That man has three Sacred Jewel\nshards in his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:22.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The shards Mukotsu and Kyokotsu had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:30.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I wondered why\nyou were so feisty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku must have given him\nthe Sacred Jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! Leave it to Naraku to\nrevive a bunch of murderers like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, and he told us to use the power\nof the Sacred Jewel shards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to kill every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine! Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're locked together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:09.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they evenly matched?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome? Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where're you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look out for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's safe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll compliment you for\nsaving Kagome at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need your thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and hide somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're after the Shikon Jewel shards\nin my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:52.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Renkotsu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who stole the shards\nfrom me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He still has them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl can see\nthe Sacred Jewel shards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:10.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Bankotsu finds out that I kept\nquiet about them,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}there'll be hell to pay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ginkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?!\N- Run, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill her in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those cannonballs\nwon't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's away from the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must get the shards back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He took my Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't let you go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:02.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't stand doctors and monks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a doctor yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:17.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again!\NEveryone's so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the only one left for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no fun fighting a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:34.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Being a half-demon,\nyou're stronger than a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why couldn't Naraku beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that all you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you know where Naraku is,\ntell me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like to be questioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you want to know\NNaraku's {\i1}whereabouts....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:21.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a large mountain,\nisn't it, Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did I have to come\nto a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:34.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei is a sacred mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:39.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so pure, demons have a hard\ntime approaching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, you don't feel anything\nbecause you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I feel like I'm\nbeing dragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:46.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go further and\nexplore, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:53.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't she listening to\nanything I said?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Hey....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Hey....no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't go further!\NI'm going this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:13.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way a mass of evil\nlike Naraku would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So why would Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A sacred barrier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get near.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku had a servant...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came here following\nthe scent of that boy, Kohaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the scent stopped.\NLike it was cut off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to get away from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope he comes\nto rescue us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:06.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake!\NIt's Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, don't go off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru will scold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was so close to\nbeing purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I get\nto see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Last time, we didn't part\nin a nice way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go back. This is no place for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go back slowly.\NBefore they notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry! If they see you,\nthey'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0} What about you, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They won't attack me.\NNow go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die! Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not if I have my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My flames of Hell\nwill roast you alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That kind of thing\nwon't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's poison insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Retreat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't bother me!\NI want to deal with them first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a\nlittle more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the Wind Scar?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You scarred my Banryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job, Ginkotsu.\NYou saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! I heard you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Break's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just that girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before she says too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:47.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Renkotsu!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He really wants us back quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:34.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!\NPlease forgive me, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin ran off before I could stop {\i1}her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,inside the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you enter sacred grounds,\nyou'll instantly be purifed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence!\NLook behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:13.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku was inside, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell the truth. You can't deceive\NLord Sesshomaru's keen nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does Lord Sesshomaru intend\nto kill Kohaku, after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} Kohaku helped\nme escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There were lots and lots\nof demons in the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:40.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku protected me\nfrom the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Demons inside this\nsacred place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's trick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:05.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I give you credit for\ncoming this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, this Naraku {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What else?\NIt's one of his demon puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buying time for the\NBand of Seven to make their escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What's this...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a demon puppet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. It has to be a decoy\nthat Naraku created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you ask, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one is different\nfrom the others he's used.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't got time\nfor fakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gotten so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll just {\i1}use....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't....let you....pass....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, trying to get ahead\nof us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, Mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:22.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An incompetent like you would\nonly let the Band of Seven get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can't have gone\nfar yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They won't get away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you noticed it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's something strange\nabout this demon puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somehow, it seems....clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean Naraku's\npuppet seems clean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's similar.\NIt's like Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This demon puppet smells of\nwater and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Water and flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why does Naraku's\npuppet smell like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!\NWhere'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the {\i1}hell....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:24.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can see it, Bankotsu.\NIt's Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with this air?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Made me sick the last\ntime we came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We couldn't feel it so far out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:37.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier has been\nmade stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:40.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This way, neither Inuyasha nor Koga\ncan come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:44.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it'll be tough for us, too.\NEven though we're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seems we won't have to go\nup to the base of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bankotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku.\NWho's this albino kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No mistake!\NHe's the one who killed Mukotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Inuyasha's older brother,\NSesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? So he was Inuyasha's\nolder brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are to go after him\nand kill him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were in the midst of\nfighting Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you had continued fighting,\nyou would have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your halberd cannot\ndefeat Inuyasha's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean because of this\nscratch on Banryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This scratch {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can become much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:19:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Renkotsu.\NHand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:19.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That you took Sacred Jewel shards from\nthat girl, Kagome, and hid them from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or should I cut the shard\nout of your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be mad, Big Brother.\NI've been meaning to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a wise decision, Renkotsu.\NYou're smart, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember that there won't be\na second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! {\i1}Suikotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And {\i1}Jakotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get this Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not happy? I thought you\nliked handsome men?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,\NI want Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a one-sided love.\NForget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}\NThis is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know where Inuyasha\nis headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ninja are clever, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn half-demon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wash your neck and\nwait for your death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:40.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look for water?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do we look for\nrivers and marshes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup. Until we find the same\nkind of water and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the same smell of {\i1}flowers....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the first time\NI ever smelled that flower scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we keep following Naraku,\nthey'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku, we'll find you\nwithout fail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:48.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei's barrier has\nbecome even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:51.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The clean scent of water and flowers\nlingered from Naraku's demon puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there some connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hijiri {\i1}Island....a{\i0} sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's said that a century ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,an illustrious monk became a\NLiving Buddha and is enshrined there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:04.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It bothers me!\NLet's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha: "Floating on the Water:\NThe Barrier of Hijiri Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why? Why can't I use\nmy Wind Scar?!
